title._content: Louise Johnson talks with Walter Schroeder, 1950

description._content: Original Collection: Extension and Experiment Station Communications Photograph Collection (P 120) Item Number: P120:2872 Image Description: Walter Schroeder, Coos County 4-H club agent, talks with Louise Johnson of Coquille, Oregon, who was president of her living organization during the 35th annual 4-H Summer School on the OSC campus.
